  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT MY OTHER GAMES!</h1><p><br><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short horror game where you pilot a tiny spaceship through turbulent \"waters\" surrounding a supermassive blackhole. Retrieve and scan sites of interest while managing your noise footprint.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/3691f294b1d37711f053082198e3f283.poster.avif?t=1730391162\" width=614 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/3691f294b1d37711f053082198e3f283.webm?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/3691f294b1d37711f053082198e3f283.mp4?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/36426e2e12536d40ce3805fa095e6885.poster.avif?t=1730391162\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/36426e2e12536d40ce3805fa095e6885.webm?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/36426e2e12536d40ce3805fa095e6885.mp4?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experimental minimalist gameplay, where your senses can fail at any time and anything could be lurking around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Glimpse your surroundings through the swirling murky waters surrounding a supermassive blackhole</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Navigate using an incomplete map and faulty sensors </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Horror based around building dread and paranoia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A short experience intended to be finished in under 2 hours</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/7e97ca1481822493ba3a78343a894902.poster.avif?t=1730391162\" width=590 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/7e97ca1481822493ba3a78343a894902.webm?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/7e97ca1481822493ba3a78343a894902.mp4?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Years ago, sensors discovered quite the anomaly. A swirling mass of liquid hydrogen surrounds a supermassive black hole. Heat and EM readings indicated the body were off the charts. You are manning the U.N.S. Icarus, a scout ship hosted by the carrier, U.N.S. Daedalus. Localized interference patterns were causing scanners and probes to malfunction so... the task falls to you. Deploy sensors, scan the area, and get back to the Daedalus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/31f57d133da283961f92a91546aa67e9.poster.avif?t=1730391162\" width=590 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/31f57d133da283961f92a91546aa67e9.webm?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2476040/extras/31f57d133da283961f92a91546aa67e9.mp4?t=1730391162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
